<div class="paragraph">
<p>If you create a credit note order for an order which was paid with Mollie, Mollie has to be informed about this. Make sure that the order items which are to be refunded are contained in the credit note order. You can find more information about credit note orders in general in the chapter <a href="/en/orders/managing-orders#500">Working with credit note orders</a> of the manual.</p>
